      "title": "Hunyo 22-28",
      "cardImageType": "publication",
      "url": "/wol/d/r101/lp-cv/202026168?#h=1:0-35:0",
      "imageUrl": "/wol/d/r101/lp-cv/202026168/thumbnail",
      "caption": "mwb26 Mayo p. 14",
      "content": "<header>\r\n<h1 class=\"du-fontSize--basePlus2 du-color--textSubdued\" id=\"p1\" data-pid=\"1\"><span id=\"page14\" class=\"pageNum\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-no=\"14\" data-before-text=\"14\"></span>HUNYO 22-28</h1>\r\n<h2 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-margin-top--2 du-margin-top-desktopOnly--4\" id=\"p2\" data-pid=\"2\"><a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026168/0/0\" data-bid=\"1-1\" class=\"b\"><strong>JEREMIAS 9-10</strong></a></h2>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"bodyTxt\">\r\n<h3 class=\"dc-icon--music dc-icon-size--basePlus1 dc-icon-margin-horizontal--8 du-fontSize--base du-borderStyle-top--solid du-borderColor--borderDefault du-borderWidth--2 du-padding-top--4 du-padding-top-desktopOnly--5\" id=\"p3\" data-pid=\"3\"><a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026168/0/0\"><strong>Awit 5</strong></a> <strong>ug Pag-ampo | Introduksiyon</strong> <span class=\"du-fontWeight--normal\">(1 min.)</span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt7\" class=\"du-fontSize--basePlus2 dc-icon--gem dc-icon-layout--top dc-icon-bgColor--teal-600 dc-icon-color--white dc-icon-margin-inlineEnd--8 dc-icon-padding--5 dc-icon-size--baseMinus1 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--2\">\r\n<h2 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--teal-700 du-margin-vertical--0\" id=\"p4\" data-pid=\"4\"><strong>BAHANDI GIKAN SA PULONG SA DIYOS</strong></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"tt9\" class=\"dc-bleedToArticleEdge dc-paddingToContentEdge du-bgColor--bgSecondary du-margin-top--8 du-padding-top--8 du-padding-bottom--4\">\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--teal-700 du-margin-vertical--0\" id=\"p5\" data-pid=\"5\"><strong>1. Unsa may Imong Ipanghambog?</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt11\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6\">\r\n<div id=\"tt12\" class=\"du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p6\" data-pid=\"6\">(10 min.)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id=\"p7\" data-pid=\"7\">Ayawg gamita ang imong mga abilidad ug mga nalampos aron magpabilib sa uban (<a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026168/1/0\" data-bid=\"2-1\" class=\"b\">Jer 9:23</a>; <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026168/1/0\"><em>w20.07</em> 6 ¶13-15</a>)</p>\r\n<p id=\"p8\" data-pid=\"8\">Pangitag mga kahigayonan nga makapanghambog kang Jehova (<a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026168/2/0\" data-bid=\"3-1\" class=\"b\">Jer 9:24</a>; <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026168/2/0\"><em>w25.05</em> 30 ¶14</a>)</p>\r\n<p id=\"p9\" data-pid=\"9\">Sundoga ang maayong ehemplo ni apostol Pablo sa pagkamapainubsanon (<a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026168/3/0\" data-bid=\"4-1\" class=\"b\">1Co 2:1-5</a>; <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026168/3/0\"><em>it</em> “Kaalam” ¶25-26</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"f1\" class=\"du-margin-top--8\">\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"/wol/mp/r101/lp-cv/mwb26/2026/228\" data-img-small-src=\"/wol/mp/r101/lp-cv/mwb26/2026/227\" alt=\"Brader nga nag-selfie sa atubangan sa iyang mahalon nga sports car.\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" />\r\n<figcaption class=\"figcaption\">\r\n<p id=\"p36\" data-pid=\"36\">Ang atong gipili nga ipanghambog naay epekto sa uban—maayo man o dili</p>\r\n</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--teal-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p10\" data-pid=\"10\"><strong>2. Espirituwal nga mga Bahandi</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt14\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6\">\r\n<div id=\"tt15\" class=\"du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p11\" data-pid=\"11\">(10 min.)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul class=\"du-listStyleType--none du-padding-inlineStart--0\"><li><p id=\"p12\" data-pid=\"12\"><a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026168/4/0\" data-bid=\"5-1\" class=\"b\">Jer 10:21</a>—Unsang leksiyon ang makat-onan sa Kristohanong mga tigdumala niini nga teksto? (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026168/4/0\"><em>jr</em> 133-134 ¶11-12</a>)</p>\r\n<div class=\"gen-field\" id=\"p13\" data-pid=\"13\">\r\n<label for=\"tt20\" id=\"tt18\" class=\"dc-screenReaderText\">Imong tubag</label>\r\n<textarea id=\"tt20\" name=\"textarea-1\"></textarea>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"du-margin-top--8\"><p id=\"p14\" data-pid=\"14\">Unsang espirituwal nga mga bahandi ang imong nakat-onan sa pagbasa sa Bibliya niining semanaha?</p>\r\n<div class=\"gen-field\" id=\"p15\" data-pid=\"15\">\r\n<label for=\"tt25\" id=\"tt23\" class=\"dc-screenReaderText\">Imong tubag</label>\r\n<textarea id=\"tt25\" name=\"textarea-2\"></textarea>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--teal-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p16\" data-pid=\"16\"><strong>3. Pagbasa sa Bibliya</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt28\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p17\" data-pid=\"17\">(4 min.) <a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026168/5/0\" data-bid=\"6-1\" class=\"b\">Jer 9:13-24</a> (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026168/5/0\"><em>th</em> tun-anan 12</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"tt29\" class=\"dc-icon--wheat dc-icon-layout--top dc-icon-bgColor--gold-600 dc-icon-color--white dc-icon-margin-inlineEnd--8 dc-icon-padding--5 dc-icon-size--baseMinus1 du-fontSize--basePlus2 du-borderStyle-bottom--solid du-borderColor--borderDefault du-borderWidth--1 du-margin-top--12 du-margin-bottom--2 du-padding-bottom--2\">\r\n<h2 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--gold-700 du-margin-vertical--0\" id=\"p18\" data-pid=\"18\"><strong>MAGMAEPEKTIBO SA MINISTERYO</strong></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--gold-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p19\" data-pid=\"19\"><strong>4. Dihang Magsugod ug Panag-estorya</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt32\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p20\" data-pid=\"20\">(4 min.) IMPORMAL NGA PAGSANGYAW. (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026168/6/0\"><em>lmd</em> leksiyon 3 punto 5</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--gold-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p21\" data-pid=\"21\"><strong>5. Dihang Magsugod ug Panag-estorya</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt34\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p22\" data-pid=\"22\">(4 min.) PAGPAMALAYBALAY. (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026168/7/0\"><em>lmd</em> leksiyon 3 punto 4</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--gold-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p23\" data-pid=\"23\"><strong>6. Dihang Makig-estorya Pag-usab</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt36\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p24\" data-pid=\"24\">(4 min.) IMPORMAL NGA PAGSANGYAW. (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026168/8/0\"><em>lmd</em> leksiyon 7 punto 3</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"tt37\" class=\"dc-icon--sheep dc-icon-layout--top dc-icon-bgColor--red-600 dc-icon-color--white dc-icon-margin-inlineEnd--8 dc-icon-padding--5 dc-icon-size--baseMinus1 du-fontSize--basePlus2 du-borderStyle-bottom--solid du-borderColor--borderDefault du-borderWidth--1 du-margin-top--12 du-margin-bottom--2 du-padding-bottom--2\">\r\n<h2 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--maroon-600 du-margin-vertical--0\" id=\"p25\" data-pid=\"25\"><strong>KRISTOHANONG PAGKINABUHI</strong></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"dc-icon--music dc-icon-size--basePlus1 dc-icon-margin-horizontal--8 du-fontSize--base\" id=\"p26\" data-pid=\"26\"><a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026168/9/0\"><strong>Awit 48</strong></a></h3>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--maroon-600 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p27\" data-pid=\"27\"><strong>7. <em>Ayawg Pailad, ug Salig sa Gingharian</em> (</strong><a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026168/6/0\" data-bid=\"7-1\" class=\"b\"><strong>Jer 10:23</strong></a><strong>)</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt42\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6\">\r\n<div id=\"tt43\" class=\"du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p28\" data-pid=\"28\">(15 min.) Pakighisgot.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id=\"p29\" data-pid=\"29\"><a href=\"https://www.jw.org/finder?wtlocale=CV&amp;lank=pub-jwb-092_14_VIDEO\" data-video=\"webpubvid://?pub=jwb-092&amp;track=14&amp;langwritten=CV\"><strong>I-play ang VIDEO</strong></a><strong>.</strong> Dayon pangutan-a ang mamiminaw,</p>\r\n<ul><li><p id=\"p30\" data-pid=\"30\">  Unsay posibleng makapahuyang sa atong pagsalig sa Gingharian sa Diyos, ug unsay atong mahimo aron dili ta mailad?</p>\r\n<div class=\"gen-field\" id=\"p31\" data-pid=\"31\">\r\n<label for=\"tt49\" id=\"tt47\" class=\"dc-screenReaderText\">Imong tubag</label>\r\n<textarea id=\"tt49\" name=\"textarea-3\"></textarea>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--maroon-600 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p32\" data-pid=\"32\"><strong>8. Pagtuon sa Kongregasyon sa Bibliya</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt52\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p33\" data-pid=\"33\">(30 min.) <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026168/10/0\"><em>lfb</em> leksiyon 96-97</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-borderStyle-top--solid du-borderColor--borderDefault du-borderWidth--2 du-margin-top--12 du-padding-top--4 du-padding-top-desktopOnly--5\" id=\"p34\" data-pid=\"34\"><strong>Konklusyon</strong> <span class=\"du-fontWeight--normal\">(3 min.)</span> <strong>|</strong> <span class=\"dc-icon--music dc-icon-size--basePlus1 dc-icon-margin-inlineStart--2 dc-icon-margin-inlineEnd--8\"><a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026168/11/0\"><strong>Awit 58</strong></a></span> <strong>ug Pag-ampo</strong></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n",
